								"__type" : "textStyle"
							},
							"string" : "Instead of `column:text:`, send `column:icon:`. The second parameter can be a block taking the item as an argument and returning any element.  {{gtMethod:IceWorkingCopy>>#gtPackagesFor:|label=Here's an example}}:\nThe status column is populated with the result of {{gtMethod:IcePackage>>#gtPackageStatus}}, which returns either a button or a label."
