				"paragraphStyle" : {
					"__type" : "textStyle"
				},
				"string" : "There are a few approaches to emulate ([asked Feenk](https://discord.com/channels/729445214812504107/735945764597006466/1479959406761349283) to compare the different approches on Discord on 3/7/2026):"
			}
